Telkom has launched its Big Deal for February 2019, offering users a fixed-LTE package at a discounted price. The SmartBroadband Wireless plan on special offers users the following: Telkom said that stock of the deal is limited, and the price is available until 28 February 2019. The company stated that users must check whether they are in an appropriate LTE coverage area before ordering the deal. A video detailing the Telkom Big Deal is posted below. <span data-mce-type="bookmark" style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; overflow: hidden; line-height: 0;" class="mce_SELRES_start">﻿</span>